UML:TaggedValue.value: Search can be done by tags
Search will be done using context of the registered user (geographic location, needs etc)
Any user on the Internet (including non-registered ones) is allowed to search uStore.
Search can be done by categories combined with text search
User, that has updated his AAL platform profile, can search in Ustore for updates on all his environment (software/hardware)
Any role can search services in uStore using regular text search (like Google)
User can search for training courses by free-text search or by associating to selected services
